data.description: Incredible home under $400K in Star, Idaho! This lovely home is tucked into a peaceful and established neighborhood in Star, close to all amenities. Split bedroom layout with a large primary bedroom, 2 secondary bedrooms, plus a true office with built-in shelving and French doors. Master en-suite has walk-in closet, dual vanities, enclosed toilet, and plenty of storage. Spacious 3 car garage to house all the vehicles & toys or extra storage. Open & bright with vaulted ceilings. Fully fenced back yard with an extended covered patio to enjoy comfortable outdoor time. HVAC system fully replaced 4 years ago, roof is also newer. Water softener system also comes with the home. Come and enjoy the serenity of Star, Idaho – and be a short drive to anything in the Treasure Valley. HOA dues include pressurized irrigation. Address may be eligible for USDA loan = 0% down, ask your lender for details on this.
